title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_1
tags:
---
Rojul: The sun's leaning west now.
Rojul: Time to lean with it.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_2
tags:
---
Rojul: Afternoon light feels different.
Rojul: Warmer. Wiser.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_3
tags:
---
Rojul: I’ve always liked the shadows in the afternoon.
Rojul: They stretch out like they’re trying to tell stories.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_4
tags:
---
Rojul: The breeze is back.
Rojul: Took its sweet time, but I forgive it.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_5
tags:
---
Rojul: I think the birds are napping.
Rojul: Even the plain needs a little quiet sometimes.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_6
tags:
---
Rojul: I patched up the old fence this afternoon.
Rojul: Not because it needed it—just because I could.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_7
tags:
---
Rojul: Afternoon is when I like to walk.
Rojul: Not too hot, not too dim. Just right.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_8
tags:
---
Rojul: The clouds drift slower in the afternoon.
Rojul: Or maybe I just notice them more.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_9
tags:
---
Rojul: There’s something kind about the afternoon sun.
Rojul: Like it’s making sure you got through the day alright.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_10
tags:
---
Rojul: I used to be all gears and duty.
Rojul: Now I’m just gears and peace.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_11
tags:
---
Rojul: The heat’s easing off now.
Rojul: Like the land’s letting out a long breath.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_12
tags:
---
Rojul: I saw a rabbit hop by just now.
Rojul: We nodded at each other, like neighbors do.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_13
tags:
---
Rojul: Afternoon is a good time for fixing small things.
Rojul: Or for not fixing anything at all.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_14
tags:
---
Rojul: The plain smells different after noon.
Rojul: Warmer. Fuller. Like it’s been steeping in sunlight.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_afternoon_15
tags:
---
Rojul: I like how the light bends now.
Rojul: Like it’s getting ready to say goodbye, but not just yet.
===
